<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error Page</title>
    <style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff4b1f, #1fddff);
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .error-container {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .error-container h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .error-container p {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .home-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #ff4b1f;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    
    .home-button:hover {
        background-color: #ff1f5a;
    }
</style>  
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>Oops! Something went wrong.</h1>
        <p>We're sorry, but we encountered an unexpected error.</p>
        <p>Please try again later or contact support if the problem persists.</p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Go to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
